<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>纽约时报 &amp;gt; 美国 &amp;gt; 政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/spotlight/on-politics</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 22:10:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>格雷厄姆·普拉特纳什么时候会退学？这是游戏的状态。</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/08/us/politics/platner-democrats-maine-state-of-play.html</link><description>以下是我们对民主党试图罢免参议员苏珊·柯林斯的骚动所了解的情况。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 22:10:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/08/us/politics/platner-democrats-maine-state-of-play.html</guid></item><item><title>民意调查对参议院之争有何评价</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/06/us/politics/senate-polls-platner.html</link><description>我们的两名政治记者深入研究了本周的调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 22:20:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/06/us/politics/senate-polls-platner.html</guid></item><item><title>美国在严重两极分化和政治裂痕中迎来 250 岁生日</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/01/us/politics/usa-america-250-trump.html</link><description>一个两极分化严重的国家如何聚集在一起举办生日聚会？</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 21:52:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/01/us/politics/usa-america-250-trump.html</guid></item><item><title>科罗拉多州初选看点：左翼能量会继续上升吗？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/29/us/politics/colorado-primaries-what-to-watch.html</link><description>周二的初选将是对民主党反建制情绪的最新考验。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 22:14:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/29/us/politics/colorado-primaries-what-to-watch.html</guid></item><item><title>应对世界杯政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/26/us/politics/world-cup-politics-trump.html</link><description>足球锦标赛带来了大量的政治故事情节。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 21:15:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/26/us/politics/world-cup-politics-trump.html</guid></item><item><title>纽约初选后，民主党面临五个大问题</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/24/us/politics/new-york-primary-election-democrats-midterms.html</link><description>反建制左翼势力激增。党的领导人有多动摇？</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 17:48:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/24/us/politics/new-york-primary-election-democrats-midterms.html</guid></item><item><title>纽约会进一步左倾吗？这是周二初选的预览。</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/22/us/politics/new-york-primaries-preview.html</link><description>该市充满戏剧性、高支出的初选将提供进步势头和市长佐兰·马姆达尼影响力的线索。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 20:06:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/22/us/politics/new-york-primaries-preview.html</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在佐治亚州的人能打败乔恩·奥索夫吗？</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/17/us/politics/ossoff-collins-georgia-senate.html</link><description>众议员迈克·柯林斯 (Mike Collins) 在一场艰苦的共和党初选中获胜，意味着参议院的一场重大对决现已确定。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 17:34:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/17/us/politics/ossoff-collins-georgia-senate.html</guid></item><item><title>阿拉巴马州和佐治亚州决选将对特朗普明天的影响力进行新的考验</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/15/us/politics/georgia-alabama-runoff-primary-elections-trump.html</link><description>桃州以及阿拉巴马州将对特朗普的影响力进行新的考验。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 21:30:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/15/us/politics/georgia-alabama-runoff-primary-elections-trump.html</guid></item><item><title>特朗普随意的中期领导让共和党陷入困境</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/12/us/politics/trump-midterms-republicans.html</link><description>在春季充满了 MAGA 初选胜利和重新划分选区的成果之后，总统和他的政党在 6 月份的开局并不顺利。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 21:06:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/12/us/politics/trump-midterms-republicans.html</guid></item></channel></rss>